{
  "texts": [
    "With a specific focus on the performance of these models, we have achieved substantial achievements throughout this study.",
    "Additionally, we are pleased to introduce the advanced fine-tuned models collectively known as AE-GPT, which have demonstrated exceptional prowess in the extraction of AE related entities.",
    "Our work showcases the success of leveraging pretrained LLMs for inference and fine-tuning them with a customized dataset, underscoring the effectiveness and potential of this approach.",
    "In the realm of LLMs for AE NER tasks, the fine-tuned GPT-3.5-turbo model (AE-GPT) notably stood out, demonstrating superior performance compared to its competing models.",
    "Interestingly, the process of fine-tuning seemed to have a significant effect on the capabilities of certain models."
  ]
}